etected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 4:54 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 16:54 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776185703210,"__openclaw":{"id":"d08a49d5","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to check sessions_list and compare against the last known state in memory/heartbeat-state.json to detect changes."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s1ewv96nfapu_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"kinds":["agent"],"limit":20,"messageLimit":3}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s1ewv96nfapu_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"heartbeat-state DTLX QLHV session state","maxResults":3,"corpus":"memory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":430,"output":127,"totalTokens":14501,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776185703836,"responseId":"062da46828cad8367b540f3bc0b355de","__openclaw":{"id":"9acf2173","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776185423104,"sessionId":"01206ce1-7c7f-4680-9c52-300ac3b19783","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":18551,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776185329977,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775